1
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,720
To tell you the truth,

2
00:01:16,239 --> 00:01:17,959
your current physical condition isn't very good.

3
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:20,599
Even though you had plasmapheresis,

4
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,040
however,

5
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:24,440
your vital signs are getting weaker.

6
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:26,559
And the rejection in your body

7
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,080
seems to be getting more severe.

8
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,000
Your blood oxygen saturation

9
00:01:30,239 --> 00:01:32,160
is barely maintained at 95 percent.

10
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:35,040
I'm considering switching to a new medication.

11
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:35,839
Switch it.

12
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,239
As soon as possible.

13
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:38,239
Okay.

14
00:01:38,839 --> 00:01:39,839
Then let's give it a try.

15
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:41,199
You see,

16
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,839
since the patient is so proactive,

17
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,440
as your doctor,

18
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,800
I naturally have to work even harder.

19
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,040
Keep it up.

20
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,319
Keep it up.

21
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:02,279
Hello?

22
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,320
Why did you suddenly

23
00:02:09,559 --> 00:02:10,559
want to treat me to a meal?

24
00:02:10,839 --> 00:02:11,800
I heard

25
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,399
that today you stepped down

26
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:15,279
from the position of CEO.

27
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:16,759
So,

28
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:17,679
as your elder,

29
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,399
I wanted to treat you to a meal.

30
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:21,800
Why?

31
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,360
Because I want to thank you.

32
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,839
At the same time,

33
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,679
I want to tell you

34
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,440
that things have come to this point,

35
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,839
and it's not your fault.

36
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,639
Facing those who stop at nothing,

37
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,360
we can't win.

38
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:37,520
Those crazy maniacs

39
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,679
are capable of anything.

40
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:40,520
How could we possibly beat them?

41
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,880
But I wasn't a good person before either,

42
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,600
and I did a lot of very bad things.

43
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,160
Maybe this is just karma.

44
00:02:56,399 --> 00:02:57,479
Even if that's the case,

45
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,119
I still think

46
00:02:59,399 --> 00:03:01,080
you're a good kid deep down.

47
00:03:01,559 --> 00:03:02,080
You see,

48
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,759
after you took over as CEO,

49
00:03:04,279 --> 00:03:06,279
you did a lot for all of us.

50
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,880
Qi Shuai.

51
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:16,720
What's wrong?

52
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:18,520
Jia Qi just told me

53
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,279
that at the company,

54
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:21,320
she saw our chat history.

55
00:03:21,839 --> 00:03:23,520
She knows everything about Feng Ziang.

56
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,119
What?

57
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:35,839
What is it?

58
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,600
Aren't you with Lin Yaoyao?

59
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,759
Why are you calling me?

60
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,399
It's Jia Qi.

61
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:42,520
Jia Qi said she's going to Feng Ziang's house

62
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,520
to get that watch.

63
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:09,440
Okay.

64
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,479
Let's leave it at that for now.

65
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,399
Bye.

66
00:04:15,119 --> 00:04:15,880
Jia Qi.

67
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:17,920
Come in first.

68
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:43,959
Aren't you going to answer?

69
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:47,079
There's no need to answer this kind of call.

70
00:04:48,239 --> 00:04:49,079
Why are you here today?

71
00:04:52,799 --> 00:04:54,200
I have something to tell you.

72
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,279
It must be something very important

73
00:04:57,359 --> 00:04:58,720
for you to come over in person.

74
00:04:59,559 --> 00:05:00,200
What is it?

75
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,720
I heard that today

76
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,040
you're going to become the Legal Representative.

77
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,359
What about it?

78
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,799
Then is there no way for you

79
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,760
to save Feimanchi Company from bankruptcy?

80
00:05:13,679 --> 00:05:14,760
So you came to see me

81
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,279
because of the company.

82
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,160
Gu Tiancheng

83
00:05:27,559 --> 00:05:28,480
What took you so long?

84
00:05:29,119 --> 00:05:29,480
Let's go, let's go.

85
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:29,959
Hurry up.

86
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:30,600
Wait.

87
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,760
Calm down, Gu Tiancheng.

88
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:33,760
Jia Qi is already at Feng Ziang's house.

89
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,799
If we rush in now,

90
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,079
it's called trespassing, got it?

91
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,160
It's illegal.

92
00:05:39,239 --> 00:05:40,079
But what if Jia Qi...

93
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,320
What if she blows her cover?

94
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:43,559
Feng Ziang is a murderer.

95
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,200
I can't take any risks.

96
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,519
Let's just go up.

97
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,519
If we go in now,

98
00:05:48,679 --> 00:05:49,600
that's when Jia Qi will blow her cover.

99
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,119
Understand?

100
00:05:50,359 --> 00:05:51,119
Then what do you suggest?

101
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,679
Do you guys trust me?

102
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:56,399
Nonsense.

103
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,200
Why would I call you if I didn't?

104
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:58,920
Good.

105
00:05:59,200 --> 00:05:59,760
Trust me.

106
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,600
Now come with me to find Feng Ziang's car.

107
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:02,559
Why find his car?

108
00:06:03,119 --> 00:06:03,959
Why ask so many questions?

109
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:04,519
Let's go.

110
00:06:04,839 --> 00:06:05,279
Go.

111
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,559
Excuse me, I need to take this call.

112
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,399
No problem.

113
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,279
Hello?

114
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:17,880
It's me.

115
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,600
What?

116
00:06:22,359 --> 00:06:23,160
I'll go down right now.

117
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:28,839
Jia Qi, I need to go downstairs for a bit.

118
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,399
Property management just called and said

119
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:32,119
there's an issue at my garage.

120
00:06:32,799 --> 00:06:33,480
Wait for me a moment.

121
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,399
It's fine.

122
00:07:22,799 --> 00:07:23,359
Darn it.

123
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,600
Darn it.

124
00:07:25,079 --> 00:07:26,640
Is this your diversion tactic?

125
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:29,679
What's wrong?

126
00:07:30,119 --> 00:07:30,920
We should have taken the chance

127
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,959
when he just came down

128
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:33,519
to rush up and save Jia Qi!

129
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,679
Are you stupid?

130
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:36,119
Jia Qi wasn't kidnapped.

131
00:07:36,119 --> 00:07:37,079
There's no one to save.

132
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,359
Jia Qi.

133
00:08:22,799 --> 00:08:23,440
I'm sorry.

134
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,640
I kept you waiting so long.

135
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:25,799
It's okay.

136
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,359
Did I take up too much of your time?

137
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,399
I'll get going now.

138
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,519
Don't you have to go to court this afternoon?

139
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,239
Jia Qi.

140
00:08:50,599 --> 00:08:52,200
I used to take you home every time.

141
00:08:53,239 --> 00:08:54,159
Not taking you home this time

142
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,039
feels a bit strange.

143
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,919
I know you came to see me this time

144
00:09:00,479 --> 00:09:01,840
not for company matters.

145
00:09:02,599 --> 00:09:04,200
But whatever the real reason is,

146
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:07,080
I have to be thankful for it.

147
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:09,520
It's what

148
00:09:10,479 --> 00:09:12,520
gave us these brief few minutes together.

149
00:09:14,359 --> 00:09:16,039
Even though it was just a few short minutes,

150
00:09:17,719 --> 00:09:18,880
I'm already very satisfied.

151
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,119
I'll be going then.

152
00:09:30,479 --> 00:09:30,960
How are you?

153
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,239
Are you okay?

154
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,479
Who told you to act on your own?

155
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:35,880
What if something happened to you?

156
00:09:37,239 --> 00:09:38,719
Don't rush, let her speak slowly.

157
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:43,039
I found the watch.

158
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,840
Is this it?

159
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,719
Then what are we doing here?

160
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:49,359
Either we go up and catch him, or we leave.

161
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,200
No.

162
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:50,679
Catch him?

163
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,320
There are still many procedures to follow.

164
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:54,200
We need to take this watch back first

165
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,119
for a bloodstain analysis.

166
00:09:55,479 --> 00:09:57,119
Then we can apply for an arrest warrant.

167
00:09:57,119 --> 00:09:57,559
Right.

168
00:09:57,919 --> 00:09:59,080
Isn't he going to attend

169
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,400
the Legal Administrator succession meeting later?

170
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,599
Yes.

171
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,679
So we still have time to prepare.

172
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,280
Okay, let's hurry up and go.

173
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:17,640
We got it.

174
00:10:18,719 --> 00:10:19,479
It's true.

175
00:10:19,479 --> 00:10:21,599
The blood on that watch is indeed Du Zheng's.

176
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,440
But we didn't follow protocol for evidence collection.

177
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,440
It's legally flawed.

178
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:26,799
Besides,

179
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:28,679
collecting evidence based on a dream...

180
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:30,320
I can't even write the report.

181
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:31,960
Even if I did,

182
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,919
it would probably cause issues in court.

183
00:10:34,359 --> 00:10:35,679
You really are an idiot.

184
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:38,479
Didn't we already find the scrapped car from the accident?

185
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,440
And isn't there blood on the front of the car?

186
00:10:40,719 --> 00:10:41,840
All we need to do is extract

187
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,359
the blood from the front of the car

188
00:10:43,359 --> 00:10:44,559
and Uncle Du's blood

189
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:46,200
to do a paternity test.

190
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,400
As long as we prove they are biological father and son,

191
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,799
wouldn't the evidence be solid?

192
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,320
Right.

193
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:55,039
Should we return the watch or...

194
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:56,320
Return it, my ass!

195
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,719
Hurry up and hand the watch over to the bureau.

196
00:10:57,719 --> 00:10:59,320
Write a self-criticism and wait for your punishment.

197
00:11:00,479 --> 00:11:01,799
It's not like we stole it.

198
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,840
What are you doing?

199
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,599
Why are you still standing there?

200
00:11:04,599 --> 00:11:05,359
Hurry up

201
00:11:05,359 --> 00:11:06,760
and go apply for an arrest warrant!

202
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,359
So should I write the self-criticism first,

203
00:11:08,359 --> 00:11:09,559
or apply for the arrest warrant first?

204
00:11:12,479 --> 00:11:13,200
Okay, okay, okay.

205
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,119
Mr. Feng.

206
00:11:22,479 --> 00:11:23,239
Congratulations on becoming

207
00:11:23,239 --> 00:11:24,599
the Legal Administrator of Feimanchi Company.

208
00:11:25,359 --> 00:11:26,960
Could you share your thoughts with us?

209
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:28,880
I already feel

210
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,640
the heavy responsibility on my shoulders.

211
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,200
I will do everything I can

212
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:34,880
to get Feimanchi back on track.

213
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,520
Do you have a recovery plan in place?

214
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:39,880
We have a preliminary plan.

215
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,000
The detailed arrangements

216
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,919
will be shared with the media later.

217
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:45,799
Mr. Feng,

218
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:47,080
as Feimanchi's

219
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,119
youngest executive,

220
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:49,080
and at the same time,

221
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,679
a top executive at Rosenmoss Company,

222
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,760
do you have any success stories

223
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:53,840
to share with everyone?

224
00:11:55,479 --> 00:11:56,559
Actually, regarding this question...

225
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:58,440
Feng Ziang.

226
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,679
This is an arrest warrant

227
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,000
based on Tan Feng's testimony

228
00:12:02,359 --> 00:12:04,000
and the scrapyard owner's testimony

229
00:12:04,239 --> 00:12:05,719
that we applied for.

230
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:08,719
What are you waiting for?

231
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:09,640
Take him away.

232
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:10,760
Impossible.

233
00:12:11,599 --> 00:12:12,200
This is absolutely impossible.

234
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,679
I don't believe it.

235
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:17,559
Gu Tiancheng!

236
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:19,000
I won't let you get away with this!

237
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:19,679
Move.

238
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:24,760
Gao Ming, let's go.

239
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,640
Okay.

240
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:34,200
Nelson.

241
00:12:35,799 --> 00:12:38,000
The scene you made taking down Feng Ziang

242
00:12:38,239 --> 00:12:39,359
was a bit too dramatic, wasn't it?

243
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:41,440
By the way,

244
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:44,760
to us at Rosenmoss Company,

245
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:47,080
he is nothing.

246
00:12:47,679 --> 00:12:48,960
We wouldn't even

247
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,239
blink an eye.

248
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:51,679
Yeah.

249
00:12:52,799 --> 00:12:53,760
Then someone like me,

250
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:56,039
who is also nothing,

251
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,599
has now come back with a vengeance.

252
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,359
What do you mean?

253
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,119
Even if I die,

254
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,599
I'll drag you down with me.

255
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:06,840
What are you trying to do?

256
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:08,440
When the time comes,

257
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,359
you don't need to worry about me.

258
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,000
What?

259
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,400
Once I finish compiling the documents,

260
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,280
I will turn myself in.

261
00:13:17,919 --> 00:13:19,520
I will expose how Rosenmoss Company sent me

262
00:13:20,119 --> 00:13:21,679
to put Feimanchi in a crisis,

263
00:13:22,559 --> 00:13:23,159
as well as

264
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,599
intentionally creating financial difficulties,

265
00:13:26,479 --> 00:13:27,520
to the media.

266
00:13:28,679 --> 00:13:29,960
Once the lawsuit begins,

267
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:32,320
you will represent Feimanchi Company

268
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,960
and claim financial compensation from Rosenmoss Company.

269
00:13:37,039 --> 00:13:37,960
You can't, Mr. Gu.

270
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,479
You'll go to jail for this.

271
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:40,840
It's equivalent to admitting

272
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,479
that you used unfair competition tactics.

273
00:13:43,119 --> 00:13:44,679
Then all your shares in the company

274
00:13:44,679 --> 00:13:45,479
will be voided.

275
00:13:45,799 --> 00:13:46,640
When that time comes,

276
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,479
I'll be taking responsibility for my actions.

277
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:49,919
Saving the company is the priority.

278
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,039
Cheer up.

279
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:20,159
Don't look so gloomy all the time.

280
00:14:30,119 --> 00:14:31,200
Take good care of yourself.

281
00:14:32,919 --> 00:14:33,640
I'll wait for you.

282
00:14:34,239 --> 00:14:34,840
Okay.

283
00:14:36,159 --> 00:14:36,880
Don't worry.

284
00:14:37,599 --> 00:14:38,520
Even if it's just for you,

285
00:14:39,159 --> 00:14:40,520
I will take good care of myself.

286
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:43,080
Mr. Gu, let's go.

287
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,000
Give me a smile.

288
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:55,080
Our Jia Qi looks best when she smiles.

289
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,479
I'm off.

290
00:15:19,559 --> 00:15:20,280
Feng Ziang,

291
00:15:20,719 --> 00:15:21,599
the thugs who beat up Tan Feng

292
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:23,599
and attacked Gu Tiancheng

293
00:15:23,599 --> 00:15:24,400
have already confessed.

294
00:15:25,039 --> 00:15:26,679
You were the one who ordered them to do it.

295
00:15:27,719 --> 00:15:28,640
What else do you have to say?

296
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,479
Murder,

297
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:32,559
instigating assault...

298
00:15:35,679 --> 00:15:36,440
Feng Ziang,

299
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,919
let me tell you,

300
00:15:38,679 --> 00:15:39,520
the relevant authorities

301
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,640
have already started

302
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:43,080
reinvestigating the substandard materials incident.

303
00:15:43,799 --> 00:15:45,039
And as for your previous

304
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:47,000
unfair competition practices...

305
00:15:47,719 --> 00:15:48,359
How could this be?

306
00:15:49,799 --> 00:15:50,840
You don't know yet, do you?

307
00:15:51,919 --> 00:15:53,440
Rosenmoss Company

308
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:55,200
chose you to take the fall.

309
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:57,599
They've already started investigating you.

310
00:16:04,799 --> 00:16:05,760
You also submitted

311
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:08,440
a diagnosis from your attending doctor at Taikang Hospital.

312
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:09,840
That's right.

313
00:16:10,599 --> 00:16:12,000
I just got it recently.

314
00:16:12,559 --> 00:16:13,960
It was also my attending doctor's idea.

315
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,799
Judging from this diagnosis,

316
00:16:18,239 --> 00:16:19,719
your condition is quite serious.

317
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:20,880
We

318
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:21,799
will verify it carefully.

319
00:16:22,599 --> 00:16:23,280
How about this?

320
00:16:23,599 --> 00:16:25,880
We'll wrap up the investigation quickly.

321
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:28,080
Since you've confessed to all the crimes anyway,

322
00:16:28,479 --> 00:16:29,359
there's no need to drag this out.

323
00:16:30,559 --> 00:16:31,080
Okay.

324
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:44,719
Jia Qi, Jia Qi!

325
00:16:47,479 --> 00:16:48,640
CEO Gu's verdict is out.

326
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:50,559
He was sentenced to two years in prison,

327
00:16:50,799 --> 00:16:51,799
with a three-year probation.

328
00:16:52,479 --> 00:16:53,320
What does that mean?

329
00:16:53,719 --> 00:16:54,320
It means

330
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:55,679
CEO Gu will be out soon.

331
00:16:56,599 --> 00:16:57,280
Really?

332
00:16:58,799 --> 00:17:00,520
Jia Qi, you can finally rest easy.

333
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,760
But...

334
00:17:03,119 --> 00:17:04,359
among the probation details,

335
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:05,599
one of the reasons is

336
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:07,160
deteriorating health.

337
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,040
Deteriorating health?

338
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:13,479
Regarding the defendant, Gu Tiancheng,

339
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:16,000
in the case of unfair competition,

340
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:17,199
the verdict is as follows.

341
00:17:18,199 --> 00:17:19,439
The defendant has pleaded guilty,

342
00:17:19,959 --> 00:17:21,359
and considering he turned himself in,

343
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,839
and for the sake of the company,

344
00:17:22,959 --> 00:17:24,719
surrendered all his assets

345
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:28,119
CEO Gu, take a rest first.

346
00:17:28,319 --> 00:17:29,119
I'll go get the car.

347
00:17:38,479 --> 00:17:40,439
striving to minimize the damage.

348
00:17:40,959 --> 00:17:41,479
Furthermore,

349
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:42,839
considering the defendant,

350
00:17:42,839 --> 00:17:44,839
after his heart transplant surgery,

351
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:47,719
is experiencing severe immune rejection,

352
00:17:48,239 --> 00:17:50,599
he is sentenced to two years in prison

353
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,160
with a three-year probation.

354
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,160
Your health is in such a state,

355
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:01,560
yet you went to the summons alone.

356
00:18:02,719 --> 00:18:03,640
Is your mental fortitude

357
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,119
so good that you don't need friends?

358
00:18:06,599 --> 00:18:07,560
It's alright.

359
00:18:10,359 --> 00:18:11,959
You never considered me a friend, did you?

360
00:18:14,239 --> 00:18:15,520
If I had told you,

361
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:17,319
would you have let me go?

362
00:18:18,239 --> 00:18:18,719
Right.

363
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:20,199
We're just superiors and subordinates.

364
00:18:20,199 --> 00:18:20,719
Right?

365
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:22,000
Wherever CEO Gu wants to go,

366
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,359
could I possibly stop you?

367
00:18:24,319 --> 00:18:25,560
That's not what I meant.

368
00:18:34,520 --> 00:18:35,160
Bear with it.

369
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:35,959
We're going to the hospital right now.

370
00:18:36,719 --> 00:18:37,920
No, don't.

371
00:18:40,439 --> 00:18:41,160
What's wrong?

372
00:18:43,479 --> 00:18:44,839
I need to go somewhere first.

373
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,880
I'm on the steps right now.

374
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:57,800
Come quickly.

375
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:06,199
Tiancheng!

376
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:07,000
Tiancheng!

377
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,319
What's wrong with you?

378
00:19:14,719 --> 00:19:15,400
You're here.

379
00:19:16,319 --> 00:19:17,319
What exactly is going on?

380
00:19:17,800 --> 00:19:19,280
I heard your health deteriorated.

381
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:20,760
No.

382
00:19:21,439 --> 00:19:22,359
I'm perfectly fine.

383
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,000
I just wanted to see

384
00:19:26,119 --> 00:19:27,319
how worried you were about me.

385
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:29,079
You don't look well at all.

386
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,199
With you by my side,

387
00:19:37,119 --> 00:19:38,520
how could I dare to deteriorate?

388
00:19:42,760 --> 00:19:43,560
Tiancheng!

389
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:45,239
Tiancheng!

390
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:53,680
Increase to 300.

391
00:19:55,319 --> 00:19:56,000
Clear!

392
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:58,599
Clear!

393
00:20:00,199 --> 00:20:01,000
Increase again.

394
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:02,959
It's at maximum energy.

395
00:20:21,479 --> 00:20:22,239
Where is Yaoyao?

396
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,680
In the blink of an eye, a few months passed.

397
00:20:43,439 --> 00:20:44,880
No matter what happened,

398
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:47,359
everyone's life goes on.

399
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,560
The Earth

400
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:51,920
is still rotating and revolving.

401
00:20:56,199 --> 00:20:56,880
Shi Hui,

402
00:20:57,719 --> 00:20:58,479
what are you doing here?

403
00:20:58,479 --> 00:20:59,959
Things are a mess for Sister Jia Qi right now.

404
00:21:00,319 --> 00:21:01,239
That manager said

405
00:21:01,239 --> 00:21:02,439
there was a scheduling error.

406
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,719
There's a problem now.

407
00:21:04,599 --> 00:21:05,199
Where are they?

408
00:21:05,599 --> 00:21:06,400
Over there.

409
00:21:11,199 --> 00:21:11,920
I'm very sorry.

410
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,079
There's a slight problem with your reservation.

411
00:21:14,079 --> 00:21:15,479
How could such a problem occur?

412
00:21:16,239 --> 00:21:17,439
What kind of issue is it?

413
00:21:17,439 --> 00:21:19,079
I'm truly sorry, Mr. Qi.

414
00:21:19,239 --> 00:21:20,839
This is indeed our hotel's mistake.

415
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:21,920
To compensate you,

416
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:22,839
you can hold

417
00:21:22,839 --> 00:21:25,040
your engagement party in our outdoor garden.

418
00:21:25,359 --> 00:21:27,479
The outdoor garden?

419
00:21:29,199 --> 00:21:29,920
Honey,

420
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,520
this outdoor garden...

421
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:32,719
are you okay with that?

422
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:34,199
Well,

423
00:21:34,839 --> 00:21:36,040
then we have to go take a look.

424
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:37,119
Right.

425
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:38,640
Can we go see it?

426
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,040
Okay, please follow me.

427
00:21:40,359 --> 00:21:41,520
Let's go, Jia Qi.

428
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:42,880
Look at what you're wearing.

429
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,839
So beautiful.

430
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:47,680
You look absolutely gorgeous today.

431
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,319
This way, please.

432
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:54,599
Please.

433
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,040
Jia Qi,

434
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:08,439
look.

435
00:22:47,479 --> 00:22:48,040
Okay.

436
00:22:48,439 --> 00:22:49,079
Now,

437
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:50,040
let's invite

438
00:22:50,079 --> 00:22:51,079
the couple

439
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:52,119
to exchange

440
00:22:52,359 --> 00:22:54,079
their tokens of love.

441
00:23:05,359 --> 00:23:06,119
Jealous?

442
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:24,280
The ceremony is complete!

443
00:23:24,839 --> 00:23:26,000
Congratulations!

444
00:23:28,239 --> 00:23:29,079
Congratulations!

445
00:23:30,199 --> 00:23:31,359
Wishing you a lifetime of happiness!
